title: Chinese president bats for cooperative cyber space
text: Chinese president bats for cooperative cyber space Thursday, 24 September 2015 (29 minutes ago) Washington , Sep 24 : Beijing advocates the building of a peaceful, secure, open and cooperative cyber space, Chinese President Xi Jinping said on Thursday.
